about supply and "command"?

01:59.330 --> 02:00.599
I mean, it's easy.

02:00.600 --> 02:02.200
I want those numbers going up, not down.

02:02.270 --> 02:03.870
And if you can't... Sorry.

02:03.930 --> 02:06.330
