14:45.500 --> 14:47.900
A small cow you can be friends with.

14:47.960 --> 14:50.300
Tell them about giraffes.

14:50.370 --> 14:52.570
What's a giraffe?

14:52.640 --> 14:54.369
It's just a tall dog with...

14:54.370 --> 14:55.970
Louder. Speak up.

14:56.040 --> 14:59.770
Tall dog with a leg for a neck.

14:59.840 --> 15:01.710
What is going on? What is happening?

15:01.780 --> 15:04.250
Are... Are these real animals?

15:04.310 --> 15:06.850
You made all these things?

15:06.920 --> 15:10.120
