15:35.010 --> 15:36.550
and they just do whatever they want.

15:36.610 --> 15:37.610
What do you mean?

15:37.611 --> 15:39.150
He gave them free will.

15:39.220 --> 15:42.220
Son, is this true?

15:42.290 --> 15:44.150
Why would you do that?

15:44.220 --> 15:46.090
I thought it would make them happy.

15:46.160 --> 15:47.690
I thought, with all that freedom,

15:47.760 --> 15:50.490
they... they could do great things.

15:52.030 --> 15:56.100
Instead, they... they
just mostly ended up...

15:56.170 --> 15:57.870
like me.

15:59.970 --> 16:01.600
Ah...

16:10.310 --> 16:14.649
It was supposed to be better.

