17:28.160 --> 17:30.959
W-Well, I kind of do, now.

17:32.830 --> 17:35.760
Okay, fine. So, um...

17:35.830 --> 17:37.569
I'm going home.

17:37.570 --> 17:39.300
Okay, fine. Go home.

17:39.370 --> 17:41.040
I'll go home. We'll both go home.

17:42.840 --> 17:44.170
Okay.

17:44.240 --> 17:45.910
Good night.

17:45.980 --> 17:47.780
Okay.

17:47.850 --> 17:49.310
Bye.

17:58.060 --> 18:00.060
Goodbye.

