18:18.410 --> 18:20.540
I know my planet is weird.

18:20.610 --> 18:23.150
I mean, it's frozen
on the top and bottom,

18:23.210 --> 18:25.680
and the sky changes colors,

18:25.750 --> 18:27.950
and people, they don't
know what they're doing,

18:28.020 --> 18:29.219
and they mess up a lot.

18:29.220 --> 18:31.220
But I love it.

18:31.290 --> 18:34.090
And I'm proud of it.

18:34.160 --> 18:36.160
And, come on. Giraffes are cool.

18:36.230 --> 18:38.090
I mean, if you don't get giraffes,

18:38.160 --> 18:40.300
if you can't find the joy

18:40.360 --> 18:42.560
in a tall dog with a leg for a neck,

18:42.630 --> 18:44.570
